title: RTVE Memoria de Espana (English Subtitles)
description: Produced by RTVE, "the PBS of Spain," Memoria de Espana is an encyclopedia of Spanish history. Spanning 23 hours of world-class video, it stretches from the geologic formation of the Iberian landmass to the 21st century-a monumental project worthy of the epic story it tells. Not available in French-speaking Canada. An RTVE Production. Spanish with English subtitles, 27-part series, 44-64 minutes each.
